vision is a single screen based app.
the main screen is called the 'view'.
top left corner has the 'v' watermark. 
  clicking defaults to [vision] view.
    [vision] view is a curated gallery of the algorithms favorite drops.
top right corner is the visionary's corner.
  visionary's corner shows users profile picture as a drop down.
    drop down menu moves diagonally to a 4/3 triangle of the screen.
      visionary's drop down is a scrollable profile view.
      tap visoinary's corner for dropdown.
      tap visionary's corner again for retract.
bottom right hand corner is the golden heart.
  each visionary or viewer can choose a proceed donation from each transaction.
    i.e. for every golden heart, comment, 
  
